Alanga nzembo Koffi Olomide azalaki te na bosambisami wa ye lundi pene na Paris na France. 
 Na nkombo na ye ya solo Antoin Agbepa, 62 ans, Olomide afundamaki mpo na kozwa babini na ye na makasi, monyokoli, kokanga na ndako mpe kosalisa bango mosola na kolanda mobeko te kati na 2002 mpe 2006.
Alukami mpe lisusu mpo afundami na France mpe na Zambie.
Baninga b aye mibale batelemaki lundi liboso ya bazuzi. Kasi bosambisi liye esalamaki na nkunku na bosengi y aba avocats ya Koffi Olomide oyo awangani makambo nyonso.